{"tid":1418734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性]請停止所有互屌行為","createTime":"2019-08-05T20:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T21:19:45.000Z","uid":34063,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"da8cd197126a45b3b3c9863bd8ebc21619ebc86b","tid":1418734,"uid":34063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:04:29.000Z","msg":"其實屌黎屌去對成個運動都唔會有乜幫助<br />\n一人一句屌完就算，我當你發洩下<br />\n但唔好係到互相屌黎屌去<br />\n屌得多對場運動有冇幫助呀<br />\n建議係可以接受，但批評請盡量減少<br />\n麻煩大家唔好回望過去，睇清未來<br />\n昨天的事檢討過唔好就唔再做，請大家多討論未來既事<br />\n一直係到講隔離一個開左2鐘個鐘有過萬正評既Post對成個運動係冇幫助架<br />\n多D討論未來，例如有個幾好就係&quot;將用完既TG罐執曬去機場展&quot;等等依類Post<br />\n係唔係會對我哋場運動更有幫助呢？<br />\n<br />\n另外想講2個鐘破萬正評，攬抄巴都做唔到啦<br />\n一睇就個有問題，唔好再比人用正負評帶風向"},{"pid":"d941024b9641b8bec66a1187826bb831a50548ef","tid":1418734,"uid":6061,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:05:07.000Z","msg":"放核彈都唔割!"},{"pid":"3d4c089d2aa718e73609daa26e91cf9c46114155","tid":1418734,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:05:28.000Z","msg":"so true"},{"pid":"2b83203c80d319ecbbbfabed1f8d8004740d15cb","tid":1418734,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:06:04.000Z","msg":"建議］ p牌正負評顯示<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n目的唔係分化p牌會員<br />\n而係當你見到有大量p牌洗正負評時<br />\n要比平時更小心去做決定"},{"pid":"b5832b84d89b8cb480228a51b00876a27e675731","tid":1418734,"uid":270333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bee8e4d65b4d57cf2ca1b4d18e1210f69125d52","tid":1418734,"uid":77180,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019